import { Navbar, Col, Nav, Form, FormControl, Button, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { FaSearch } from 'react-icons/fa';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';


export default function Header () {
    return (
        <Container fluid='false' className='header-bg'>
            <Container>
                <Row className='navbar'>
                    <Col xs={2}>
                        <Link to='/'>Movie</Link>
                    </Col>
                    <Col md={8} sm={6}>
                        <Form inline className="search-form d-flex w-100">
                            <FormControl 
                                type="text"
                                placeholder="Search"
                                className="w-100"
                            />
                            <Button type="submit">
                                <FaSearch />
                            </Button>
                    </Form>
                    </Col>
                    <Col>
                        <Link className="signin">Sign in</Link>          
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </Container>
    )
}
